Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:19.71,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}將命運改寫下一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:20.65,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}開始飛翔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:26.91,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}Fly Away On A Brighter Day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:32.94,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}即便有令人咋舌難以邁開步伐的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:34.36,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}更能熱情如火
