Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:04.34,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}すぐ会いに行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:07.59,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}君の非常サインが
